{"3017630": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "鬥獸場公主", "steam_appid": 3017630, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/65471d40a0d9786940fa6242dafbbbb9.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的兒子阿爾被診斷出患有絕症。雖然有治癒的方法，但你必須踏入神秘的盧瑟溫王國尋找線索。你的妻子先行一步，卻離奇失蹤。現在，輪到你拯救家人了。揮舞你的劍，在充滿魔法的盧瑟溫大陸上奮戰，救回至親之人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/8f5906f8afb88396880be50a0a74d74c.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一款卡牌戰鬥+構築牌組遊戲。贏得戰鬥可獲得金錢，並用其購買裝備、增益效果、解鎖事件或強化卡組。挑戰競技場中的敵人，一步步登上頂尖排名，贏取珍貴的解藥。面對魅惑又強勢的女性對手，她們將利用魅力與壓倒性的戰術讓你分心。準備迎戰吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/0acf626651550b6d8722d5ffbd9828bc.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/93ecbb2d468b26636f48b43e3c99d6c8.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/4ab109d4b1a9f9767052a47357c739a1.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/2430a81359aaeec86166b8db7fd2acc6.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/7250264dec598df8c988d0c2e5129ada.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/eb4f414450eefa697fe3d9beef660c33.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/6abdc2f3a483db0dceaeb8df9ec2b920.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>資源管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >時間和金錢至關重要！你只有六個月的時間去尋找治療方法，拯救你的兒子，並救回失蹤的妻子。合理利用資金購買裝備或強化包，以增強你的卡組。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>圖鑑與戰鬥回顧</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在圖鑑中重溫你的冒險與遭遇，包括CG、H場景和音樂。注意，勝利與失敗的場景都會解鎖，所以不需要故意輸掉戰鬥（記住，時間緊迫！）。遊戲還提供了自由戰鬥模式，讓你與之前遇到的敵人再度交手。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多重結局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲根據你的選擇和戰鬥結果提供多個結局。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>繼承功能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當滿足特定條件時，遊戲的失敗將解鎖繼承功能。你可以選擇保留下一次存檔中的物品——或者從頭開始。繼承選項可能包括技能卡、屬性、裝備，甚至金錢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/65471d40a0d9786940fa6242dafbbbb9.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的兒子阿爾被診斷出患有絕症。雖然有治癒的方法，但你必須踏入神秘的盧瑟溫王國尋找線索。你的妻子先行一步，卻離奇失蹤。現在，輪到你拯救家人了。揮舞你的劍，在充滿魔法的盧瑟溫大陸上奮戰，救回至親之人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/8f5906f8afb88396880be50a0a74d74c.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一款卡牌戰鬥+構築牌組遊戲。贏得戰鬥可獲得金錢，並用其購買裝備、增益效果、解鎖事件或強化卡組。挑戰競技場中的敵人，一步步登上頂尖排名，贏取珍貴的解藥。面對魅惑又強勢的女性對手，她們將利用魅力與壓倒性的戰術讓你分心。準備迎戰吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/0acf626651550b6d8722d5ffbd9828bc.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/93ecbb2d468b26636f48b43e3c99d6c8.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/4ab109d4b1a9f9767052a47357c739a1.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/2430a81359aaeec86166b8db7fd2acc6.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/7250264dec598df8c988d0c2e5129ada.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017630/extras/eb4f414450eefa697fe3d9beef660c33.avif?t=1776345510\" width=616 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_pa